♪ Sometimes the world
looks perfect ♪

00:15.248 --> 00:17.551
♪ Nothing to rearrange ♪

00:17.584 --> 00:20.687
♪ Sometimes you just
get a feeling ♪

00:20.721 --> 00:24.791
♪ Like you need
some kind of change ♪

00:24.825 --> 00:28.629
♪ No matter what the odds
are this time ♪

00:28.662 --> 00:30.697
♪ Nothing’s going to stand
in my way ♪

00:30.731 --> 00:32.566
♪ This flame in my heart ♪

00:32.598 --> 00:34.367
♪ And a long lost friend ♪

00:34.400 --> 00:39.405
♪ Gives every dark street
a light at the end ♪

00:39.439 --> 00:42.475
♪ Standing tall ♪

00:42.509 --> 00:46.212
♪ On the wings of my dream ♪

00:46.246 --> 00:49.349
♪ Rise and fall ♪

00:49.382 --> 00:52.819
♪ On the wings of my dream ♪

